name: MPTimedMetadata
desc: A timed metadata object that carries time-based information within HTTP streamed media.

items.name: var allMetadata: [AnyHashable : Any]!
items.desc: A dictionary containing all the metadata in the object.

items.desc: The namespace of the identifying key.

items.name: var timestamp: TimeInterval
items.desc: The timestamp of the metadata, in the timebase of the media stream.

items.desc: Posted when new timed metadata arrives.
